### Adding New Dice Image Sets

To add new custom dice image sets, follow these steps:

1. Create a new directory inside the **images** directory with the color name of your choice (e.g., *green*).
2. Add six PNG files named *dice1.png*, *dice2.png*, *dice3.png*, *dice4.png*, *dice5.png*, and *dice6.png* to the new directory.
3. The <code style="color : name_color">DiceAnimator</code> class will automatically detect and load the new dice image set.
